{"type":"message","id":"fe2d45c7","parentId":"68c5e9e2","timestamp":"2026-03-23T19:52:02.968Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bcnyzl2br5jk_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5083\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3238\n[file inferred from ACTION] research/TIC-classifier.ps1\n[mutation proposed] research/TIC-classifier.ps1\n[master 4c90979] pulse: 2026-03-23 155140\n 7 files changed, 390 insertions(+), 125 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 155140.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 155140.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 153842.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 155140 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step - implementing a classifier to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis on actual pulse logs. I need to build a working prototype that can classify invariant vs variant content and attempt next-pulse prediction.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"gentle-cove","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5083\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3238\n[file inferred from ACTION] research/TIC-classifier.ps1\n[mutation proposed] research/TIC-classifier.ps1\n[master 4c90979] pulse: 2026-03-23 155140\n 7 files changed, 390 insertions(+), 125 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 155140.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 155140.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 153842.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 155140 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step - implementing a classifier to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis on actual pulse logs. I need to build a working prototype that can classify invariant vs variant content and attempt